lications if possible.\nThe structural simplifier and pattern matcher do not handle kernel projection\nterms; this preprocessing step folds them into projection function applications.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.foldProjs","kind":"def","line":257,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.foldProjs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L257-L288"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.unfoldReducible\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">unfoldReducible</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Unfolds all `reducible` declarations occurring in `e`.\nThis is meant as a preprocessing step. It does **not** guarantee maximally shared terms\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.unfoldReducible","kind":"def","line":249,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.unfoldReducible","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L249-L255"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.isUnfoldReducibleTarget\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">isUnfoldReducibleTarget</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</s