s=\"name\">SymM</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM","kind":"def","line":229,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L229-L229"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.debug\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">debug</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.debug","kind":"def","line":227,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.State.debug","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L227-L227"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.instanceOverrides\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">instanceOverrides</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Data/PersistentHashMap.html#Lean.PHashMap\">PHashMap</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Instances registered by satellite modules for types they create themselves\n(e.g., `grind linarith`'s envelope type `IntModule.OfNatModule.Q`).\n`Sym.synthInstance?` consults this table (keyed by the instance type, structural equality)\nbefore running typeclass resolution. This both skips searches whose results are known in\nadvance, and ensures the registered term is used as the canonical representative.\n\nWe currently use this table to reduce the overhead of type class resolution in `grind`.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.instanceOverrides","kind":"def","line":226,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.State.instanceOverrides","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L226-L226"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.canon\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">State</span>.<span class=\"name\">canon</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State\">State</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Canon.State\">Canon.State</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.State.canon","kind":"def","line":216,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.State.canon","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed