Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When `true`, `shareCommon` maintains the `SymM` invariant that kernel projections\nhave been folded into projection function applications: if a new term contains one,\n`shareCommon` folds it before adding the term to the table of maximally shared terms.\n`cbv` disables this check because it processes kernel projections natively.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.enforceFoldProjs","kind":"def","line":158,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.enforceFoldProjs","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L158-L158"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.enforceUnfoldReducible\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">enforceUnfoldReducible</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When `true`, `shareCommon` maintains the `SymM` invariant that reducible constants\nhave been eagerly unfolded: if a new term contains one, `shareCommon` unfolds it\nbefore adding the term to the table of maximally shared terms.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.enforceUnfoldReducible","kind":"def","line":151,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.enforceUnfoldReducible","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L151-L151"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.verbose\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">verbose</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When `true`, issues are collected during proof search and reported on failure. ","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.verbose","kind":"def","line":145,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.verbose","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L145-L145"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.mk\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Meta</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sym</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">mk</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> → <a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config\">Lean.Meta.Sym.Config</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.mk","kind":"ctor","line":142,"name":"Lean.Meta.Sym.Config.mk","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.lean#L142-L159